name: tabtab
description: tab completion helpers, for node cli programs. Inspired by npm completion.

scripts.coverage-html: npm run mocha && c8 report --reporter=html && serve coverage
scripts.api: for file in `echo index.js installer.js prompt.js`; do jsdoc2md lib/$file > api/$file.md; done
scripts.docs: npm run api && npm run readme && npm run changelog
